General.Name: GETS Global Bhd
General.Description: One Glove Group Berhad, an investment holding company, manufactures, markets, and sells examination gloves and other related activities in Malaysia, Japan, Germany, Singapore, the United States, India, and internationally. It offers nitrile powder free examination gloves; and engages in the cultivation and harvesting of oil palm fruits. The company was formerly known as GETS Global Berhad and changed its name to One Glove Group Berhad in July 2022. One Glove Group Berhad was incorporated in 2002 and is based in Kamunting, Malaysia.
